# DeFi (Decentralized Finance) - Study Notes

## ğŸ“Œ What is DeFi?
```
DeFi = Blockchain + Smart Contracts = New Financial System
```

A complete financial system that lets you:
- ğŸ’° Lend money globally and earn interest (no bank)
- âš¡ Get instant loans (no paperwork)
- ğŸ”„ Trade assets 24/7 (no broker fees)

**Core Principle:** Trust the code, not institutions

---

## ğŸ†š DeFi vs Traditional Finance

| Feature | Traditional Finance | DeFi |
|---------|-------------------|------|
| **Access** | âŒ Permissioned (ID, credit check, approval) | âœ… Permissionless (just internet) |
| **Control** | âŒ Centralized (banks can freeze accounts) | âœ… Decentralized (you control assets) |
| **Transparency** | âŒ Opaque (hidden operations) | âœ… Transparent (public blockchain) |

> **Historical Context:** 2008 crisis - banks ran out of money, couldn't honor withdrawals

