## âš™ï¸ How DeFi Works

### Smart Contracts
```javascript
// Pseudocode example
if (userDeposit >= requiredCollateral) {
    grantLoan(userAddress, loanAmount);
    // Guaranteed execution - no human approval needed
}
```

### Two Core Properties

#### 1. Deterministic Execution
```
Input â†’ Smart Contract â†’ Guaranteed Output
No bias | No bureaucracy | No surprises
```

#### 2. Composability (Money Legos)
```
Protocol A + Protocol B + Protocol C = New Financial Product
```

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Common DeFi Applications

### 1. Decentralized Exchanges (DEXs)
```
Examples: Uniswap, Curve
Function: Peer-to-peer trading
Features: No KYC, no account, no restrictions
```

### 2. Lending & Borrowing
```
Examples: Aave, Compound
- Lend assets â†’ Earn interest
- Borrow with crypto collateral
```

### 3. Derivatives & Trading
```
Example: GMX
- Leveraged perpetual trading
- Complex financial instruments
```

### 4. Yield Farming & Liquidity Mining
```
Provide liquidity â†’ Earn token rewards
```

### 5. Asset Management
```
Example: Yearn Finance
Auto-optimizes returns across protocols (DeFi robo-advisor)
```

