## ğŸª™ Tokens: The Foundation

### What are Tokens?
```typescript
interface Token {
    type: "currency" | "ownership" | "governance" | "access" | "certificate";
    programmable: true;
    composable: true;
}
```

### Token Use Cases
- ğŸ’µ Currency (money)
- ğŸ“Š Ownership (project shares)
- ğŸ—³ï¸ Voting power (governance)
- ğŸ« Access rights (membership)
- ğŸ“œ Certificates

### Why Tokens Matter
```
Tokens = Building blocks of DeFi

Used in:
â”œâ”€â”€ DEX trading
â”œâ”€â”€ Lending platforms
â”œâ”€â”€ Staking rewards
â””â”€â”€ All DeFi protocols
```

