## ğŸ¯ Why DeFi Matters

| Benefit | Impact |
|---------|--------|
| **Inclusion** | Access for 1.7B unbanked people |
| **Transparency** | Every transaction is auditable |
| **Innovation** | Open-source = rapid development |
| **Control** | You own assets, not banks |
| **Efficiency** | No middlemen = lower costs |

